title: Mariah Carey on New Year's Eve performance: 'They foiled me'

meta_data.title: Mariah Carey on New Year's Eve performance: 'They foiled me'
meta_data.description: Mariah Carey is blaming producers for her bungled performance on Dick Clark's New Year's Rockin' Eve, saying, They foiled me.Carey says on her Twitter page that the show's production team had technical issues and her ear monitors didn't work. Carey stopped
